name: JellenWedding
0:
”Alexa, ask wedding info, when is my wedding”
”Alexa, ask wedding info, how many days till my wedding”
”Alexa, ask wedding info how many days till Ellen's wedding”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: wedding info
des:
Gets wedding date when asked. Gets how many days till wedding from the current date. Gets how many days been married for from the current date.

Now our skill now has visual card which you view on your Alexa Show or in the Alexa app.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
